     "After T206 fixed the webhook, the /welcome 10s-poll TIMEOUT state almost never fires (activation now lands in ~1-2s). But its copy is contradictory: title 'All set!' (T205) sits over body 'we're a beat behind on the rest of the setup', and the 'Go to portal anyway' button -- which used to dead-end -- now actually works (the webhook DOES activate). Minor copy cleanup, low priority.",
