     "User 2026-06-09: 'we locked what every tier gets access to but did not update the radialnav.' Dug past the stale Pricing.jsx (retired one-time model) to the real lock (CLAUDE.md section 20, T096 2026-06-06): monthly subscription; Free=Strength+Cardio, CoreRX=+Bodyweight+Calories, FullRX=+Heart+Hydration+Sleep+future. The only mis-gated page was Heart (code = CoreRX; lock = FullRX), already flagged as a to-fix in the T096 ledger.",
