     "User 2026-06-09 'do it': after T138 scoped the ADMIN Nutrition Overview to my-clients, ship the same page to the coach portal (parallel to T137 for Weight Goal) so coaches get a Nutrition Overview scoped to their own roster.",
     "DONE + deployed (web live index-Dvs98TBP.js). Extracted the loader + grid into shared pieces (lib/nutritionOverview.js: loadNutritionRows + lastNDays/shortDay/complianceColor/complianceScore; components/NutritionOverviewList.jsx) and refactored AdminNutrition onto them (T138 scoping preserved). New CoachNutrition.jsx scoped to coach_id = coach.id; /coach/nutrition route registered in App.jsx; 'Nutrition Overview' nav entry (Utensils icon) added to CoachShell after Weight Goal Progress.",
